snippet.title: Dragons lair (NES) speedrun in 7:20 (PAL-version with 50hz normal speed)
snippet.description:
This equal 6.02 with 60hz speed (I used my old runs)

This is maybe my last run entire game. This went as good as i planned. There is very minor room improvement

I was very glad with this run. Im not sure going game speed still realistic comapred real PAL Nes speed, this going maybe even slower now when i changes settings with PAL mode i can,t say where i lost time with WR run, but i still not beat it.  I think most my intentions are even better than WR run

I used tons awesome risky tricks. Almost all new trick are used here. This run is very hard make any faster. Most i can haved more luck with lizard kings and Singe was quite cautions, but i just wanted survive alive.

But right now i thinking i can,t make that any faster. 

Yeah its played on emulator without cheats and used PAL emulation settings (50hz speed) Annoying i not haved this game my Nes so i can,t try serious records. But this run at least look very cool compared other ones.
